    {
      "id": "6090ec19aff09e00003c54e8",
      "text": " Additionally, we have two brand new series of courses, まずは！TOEIC基礎シリーズ [UK/AUS版] and さらに！TOEIC上級シリーズ [UK/AUS版]. In these series, you’ll find TOEIC-like sentences read by either British or Australian voices. These courses will help you practice listening to non-American pronunciation.",
